 "FindInfraLinearCombination[PathGraph[Range[7]], 1, {{2, 2}}, All]"]], \
"Input",ExpressionUUID->"b5f87d2c-84a8-44eb-9fe7-fedb3e410f96"],

Cell[BoxData[
 $CellContext`buildCell["CodeText"]], "Input",ExpressionUUID->"da53166b-ceff-4215-8424-9b869273c183"],

